{"tid":1946286,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"繼約翰遜後　英國衛生大臣夏國賢同樣確診新型肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-27T13:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T13:41:29.000Z","uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8cce4371f0c640bcd3b5bc4e1b14d25d3a8fc8","tid":1946286,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1517313_1_20200327211308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1517313_1_20200327211308.jpg&h=02ed0659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國首相約翰遜及衛生大臣夏國賢，先後對新冠病毒測試呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜在社交網站發布影片，指自己出現輕微病徵，包括發燒及持續咳嗽，經檢測證實染病，正自我隔離，會在家中透過視像會議，繼續領導政府對抗疫情的工作，又再次呼籲民眾遵守政府指示，留在家中，強調最終一定會戰勝疫情。<br />\n<br />\n衛生大臣夏國賢其後亦公布自己確診的消息，指自己出現輕微病徵，在醫生建議下接受檢測，證實呈陽性，他會在家中自我隔離，期間繼續工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517313-20200327.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517313-20200327.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fh4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=b8e42e9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517313-20200327.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=22796b58\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517313-20200327.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}